CONTENTS:                                                 
These IBIS models are for the s27ks642 devices.
These models are for 24 ball BGA package

USAGE:
The models are derived for nominal 1.8V I/O voltage supplies. 
The temperature range is -40 to 125C.
Package parasitics are included.

Refer to the model selector for the IO drive strength of interest.

Vinl and Vinh levels are VCCQ dependant and should be adjusted per datasheet

VERIFICATION
1. This model was syntax checked with IBISCHK V6.1.4
2. There are 0 parser errors and acceptable warnings.


HELP/QUESTIONS?
If there are any additional questions or concerns about using this 
model, please create a technical support case at www.cypress.com/support 
or call the technical support line at 408-943-2821 or 1-800-541-4763, 
option 8.     


